data.description: This gorgeous picture perfect newer one story home is located in one of the most sought after areas of Hollister, this home is filled with natural light from the many large windows. Fresh interior paint. Whole house water softener. Tastefully landscaed extra large lot of 8,271sqft with many verity of citrus and fruit trees, low maintenance drought resistant plants yard, pergola with large gas firepit and sitting benches perfect for parties and family gathering. RV access, extra large metal shed/sorage, immaculately well maintained home. Open family room kitchen concept boasting granite counter tops, large pantry & indoor laundry room. Close proximity  to schools, community Hospital, shopping,dining & San Justo sport facility. Easy access to Highway 156 & 25 for easy commuting to Silicon Valley.This stunner is completely upgraded and ready for you. NO HOA
